{"tid":1929420,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港鎖國","createTime":"2020-03-17T02:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T03:16:12.000Z","uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f2701614f4cef8d698e78980900c8171d724d484","tid":1929420,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:24:05.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥今早（17日）在行政會議前會見記者，表示各國確診個案近日呈爆發性上升，加上過去兩周的確診個案有九成屬輸入個案，疫情再次進入嚴峻階段，她表示今日內會向全球其他國家地區發出紅色外遊警示，內地、澳門及台灣除外。她亦宣布，本周四（19日）凌晨零時起所有抵港的人需接受14日強制檢疫及醫學監察。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f770197d1625565ec7ace31ebf238de1b619b542","tid":1929420,"uid":54510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:25:03.000Z","msg":"除大陸 有乜用"},{"pid":"54a618190f20d62b75712551171c26579c563717","tid":1929420,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:25:14.000Z","msg":"支那狗怕咗香港轉機cases"},{"pid":"4afab19c9bffd490d9a9d65326362c3bd91076e1","tid":1929420,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f770197d1625565ec7ace31ebf238de1b619b542","tid":1929420,"uid":54510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:25:03.000Z","msg":"除大陸 有乜用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:26:16.000Z","msg":"中國鎖緊（叫做）"},{"pid":"92e765f1f823c709ec4168b8da9395c952d3f9b5","tid":1929420,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}